{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 170°C. Grease a springform cake tin (24 cm) with butter, then dust with a little flour and set aside.","Place chocolate in mixing bowl and grate <nobr>8 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add caster sugar, yoghurt, milk, eggs, vanilla bean paste and 100 g butter then mix <nobr>40 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","Add potato flour, salt and 230 g plain flour then mix <nobr>20 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>.","Add yeast and mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","Transfer half the cake batter into prepared tin. Lay pear slices on top of batter, then sprinkle with cocoa powder. Transfer remaining batter into tin over the top.","Bake for 40 minutes (170°C). If the cake is browning too quickly on the top, cover with aluminium foil and return to the oven and continue cooking for a further 15-20 minutes (170°C) or until a skewer inserted in centre comes out clean. Leave cake to cool in tin, and then dust with icing sugar, slice and serve."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["150 g dark chocolate, small pieces or callets","200 g caster sugar","120 g plain yoghurt","80 g whole milk","3 medium eggs","1 tsp vanilla bean paste","100 g unsalted butter, diced, plus extra for greasing","70 g potato flour","1 pinch fine sea salt","230 g plain flour, plus extra for dusting","2 tsp dried instant yeast","2 pears, (approx. 250 g), peeled and cut into slices (1 cm)","2 Tbsp cocoa powder","2 Tbsp icing sugar, for dusting"]}],"id":"r252882","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-rVBvB60NDHs\/XZWrJcnSMWI\/AAAAAAAAfiw\/GKqxaM_MHw4am3aU4xddsk7pQ2vM2rB8gCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_cjtLHU9uA3E11-0n.png","title":"Chocolate and Pear Cake","publishedAt":"2017-09-25T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5.8 g","fat":"12.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"49 g","calories":"1393 kJ \/ 331 kcal"},"usefulItems":"spring form tin (Ø 24 cm), aluminium foil, skewer, oven","hintsAndTricks":["You can serve this cake warm if desired. Try drizzling over a warm caramel sauce for an extra decadent treat."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 30m","12 slices"]}